item.title: Download
item.description: rust-keylock is delivered as a desktop app, an Android app and a shell app. Here is how you can install what you are interested in: Desktop The desktop application can currently run on Linux (x64) and Windows (x64). Prerequisites Java 8 (or later) should be installed on your system. Installation and Usage Download the .zip or .tar.gz file. Both compressed files contain the same application, so you may select whichever suits your environment.
